Title: Journey to The Earth
DateModified: '2019-02-16'
DatePublished: '2019-02-16'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/journey-to-the-earth
SetInCountry: Portugal
Category: Making a local connection
AuthorName: Vina Adriana Widjaya
AuthorCountry: Indonesia
Text: 'Enjoy the city or country like a local. Explore, dream, discover. Start from
  the people, food, tourism spots, until hidden spots.

  Bring the camera, capture all the picture, then share it to media social. Let the
  picture talking to the people, so people can know about the country.'
